source.name: HUD USPS ZIP Code Crosswalk Files
source.description: The HUD USPS ZIP Code Crosswalk Files relate the United States Postal Service (USPS) ZIP codes to Census Bureau geographies,  so the valuable data available only at the ZIP code level can be combined with demographic data tabulated at various Census geography levels to provide new avenues of exploration.
